{"tid":1042191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《港女老婆》綠帽事件事隔一年，叮叮廣告繼續鞭屍","createTime":"2019-03-01T11:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T15:03:11.000Z","uid":236171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"415a3573cd0fd3ef11eaeb0cb72fa23a0fe31fac","tid":1042191,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:36:28.000Z","msg":"話說早前有巴絲踢爆漫畫系列《我的港女老婆》男主角 Cuson 慘被港女老婆 Caca 贈送綠帽。事隔一年，兩人離婚，臭雞再婚，Cuson 亦好爭氣咁揾到新女。<br />\n<br />\n正當我以為成件事告一段落，今日放工上到電車伸咗個懶腰... 嘩 咁大隻臭雞壓頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFE6rYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFE6rYJ.jpg&h=8c81ae62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於小弟本來唔係 Cuson 擁躉，加上都有一段時間無見過佢地，一時三刻以為認錯人。上 Facebook 揾翻，真係佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPdZMZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPdZMZ3.jpg&h=8064f15d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解發生咗成年都未拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知如果有日 Cuson 或者臭雞伉儷咁啱上翻呢班車會有咩感覺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP. S. 放工時間人多，所以相嘅角度麻麻地勿怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d63d5706a4511dc4aa9a051e0730bed02b44a06","tid":1042191,"uid":236171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"補上香港某內容農場兩個月前報道<br />\n<br />\n&quot;早已認定對方是終身伴侶&quot;<br />\n見到屌咗出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Ax0wwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ax0wwP.jpg&h=58824874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2239104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2239104%2F&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=c2cebfa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2239104/</a>"},{"pid":"7baf2c6d75f5e6e803031731d3724d7ea6787f1c","tid":1042191,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"案件重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[臭雞] 「我的港女老婆」Caca Yu偷食整合post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/544741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/544741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da284affaa49e7f7e581c8c1e0cd105c15197da3","tid":1042191,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a793c546a06d306cd401343b92e64a138e339e","tid":1042191,"uid":120655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"點解冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c12642d492fa799965802e002edc590a3c5490","tid":1042191,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a793c546a06d306cd401343b92e64a138e339e","tid":1042191,"uid":120655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"點解冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"因為啲人開始講到悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}